## Hello 
### Welcome to my personal website


This site is meant to serve as a hub for things such as projects (personal and school), resume, contact information, etc. I'll also try to provide a little more information that you typically wouldn't just get from a standard resume, especially considering this meant to assist in the job search.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
